### RBI Gap Analysis Matrix

| Topic/Issue | What RBI Says | Citation/Clause | What RBI Does NOT Say | Gap Identified |
|-------------|---------------|-----------------|----------------------|----------------|
| **Authority to Freeze** | | | | |
| When can banks freeze? | | | | |
| Who within bank can authorize? | | | | |
| What criteria trigger freeze? | | | | |
| **Procedural Requirements** | | | | |
| Notice to account holder? | | | | |
| Timing of notice? | | | | |
| Content of notice? | | | | |
| Right to explanation? | | | | |
| **Time Limits** | | | | |
